{"tid":1895782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知點樣立遺囑？","createTime":"2020-02-24T17:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T21:10:53.000Z","uid":135977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9151239435bac40ff33f5171832fc02cf3d1e3","tid":1895782,"uid":135977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"就咁搵張紙手寫？然後放喺邊？<br />\n定要搵律師俾錢？<br />\n上網搵個個都唔同講法<br />\n<br />\n同埋要咩內容？<br />\n除咗會對未死既人有影響既事（例如錢點分配）<br />\n仲有咩寫<br />\n如果啲錢喺銀行戶口洗唔洗寫戶口密碼？（我知好on9但我未寫過真係唔知sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我依家諗到得錢、器官<br />\n有冇人立過可以教一教我<br />\n唔該晒！！！"},{"pid":"82759754479f6bd068b2fb4413a7416ff8384b62","tid":1895782,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"335d5291f82e54657fa4d01f1cd709a94a1494d9","tid":1895782,"uid":135977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82759754479f6bd068b2fb4413a7416ff8384b62","tid":1895782,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"關咩事，立定先啫<br />\n如果死左無立到就好on9"},{"pid":"d70605172f7cfeaf80a96143daf2aefdada2d1be","tid":1895782,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e33bccd111d2225529f4cbd2ee1f32c4a166e272","tid":1895782,"uid":135977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d70605172f7cfeaf80a96143daf2aefdada2d1be","tid":1895782,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"335d5291f82e54657fa4d01f1cd709a94a1494d9","tid":1895782,"uid":135977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82759754479f6bd068b2fb4413a7416ff8384b62","tid":1895782,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T18:04:55.000Z","msg":"關咩事，立定先啫<br />\n如果死左無立到就好on9"},"